<item>
            <title>[LU-10772] New static analysis issues in v2_10_58_0-102-g1a5fdde</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10772</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Found 2 new static analysis issues in v2_10_58_0-102-g1a5fdde:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Suspicious dereference of pointer before NULL check&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lnet/utils/lnetconfig/cyaml.c&lt;/tt&gt;: in &lt;em&gt;free_node&lt;/em&gt;, Suspicious dereference of pointer &apos;node&apos; before NULL check at line 686&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pointer may be dereferenced after it was positively checked for NULL&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lustre/utils/lfs.c&lt;/tt&gt;: in &lt;em&gt;build_layout_from_yaml_node&lt;/em&gt;, Pointer &apos;string&apos; checked for NULL at line 2192 may be dereferenced at line 2196. Also there is one similar error on line 2207.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


